{"tid":1964394,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中時幫老豆老母裝左連登既巴絲打，你地有冇後悔？","createTime":"2020-04-08T19:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T16:43:55.000Z","uid":54930,"like":25,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"83b525e275dbdc1b502e4b61f5a3793f1eee2e93","tid":1964394,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:32:00.000Z","msg":"我好坦白講，我就冇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係冇你地咁傻教老豆老母上連登呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登低質又唔係第一日既事，唔知你地果時比咩矇蔽左雙眼，以為連登係寶，我諗呢段時間仲有上既伯父伯母應該睇到眼都凸，一係冇眼睇delete左app, 一係睇到個人變灰心撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦白d，有就有，冇就冇，如果你係好似我咁醒既，歡迎留言加入恥笑班傻仔<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362d67d1dfb75a52eb380cbd123c9d8decadb4a1","tid":1964394,"uid":104698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:38:45.000Z","msg":"同意呀<br />\n<br />\n訓左冇睇 想問依家係咪贏左？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1964393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1964393</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c954ffcaac67b513b5c697eb4331934c7e5b572d","tid":1964394,"uid":54930,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:44:10.000Z","msg":"囝/囡：阿媽，呢個連登好野黎架，可以睇到好多反送中資訊<br />\n伯母：好呀，等我試下先<br />\n連登仔：所有女人都係雞<br />\n伯母：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8035256db23c4a9f8415e43e7071ab7a8750